org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.adapter

Interface InternalAdapterStore

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    InternalAdapterStoreImpl, JobContextInternalAdapterStore

    public interface InternalAdapterStore
    This is responsible for persisting adapter/Internal Adapter mappings (either in memory or to disk depending on the implementation).
